The following compression algorithms in this project are independent
TypeScript reimplementations inspired by their Python counterparts
in the Headroom project:

  - SmartCrusher (headroom/transforms/smart_crusher.py)
  - CodeCompressor (headroom/transforms/code_compressor.py)
  - LogCompressor (headroom/transforms/log_compressor.py)
  - DiffCompressor (headroom/transforms/diff_compressor.py)
  - SearchCompressor (headroom/transforms/search_compressor.py)
  - ContentDetector (headroom/transforms/content_detector.py)
  - CacheAligner (headroom/transforms/cache_aligner.py)
  - CCR Store (headroom/cache/compression_store.py)
  - TOIN (headroom/telemetry/toin.py)
  - Output Shaper (headroom/proxy/output_shaper.py)
  - Read Lifecycle (headroom/transforms/read_lifecycle.py)
  - Kompress ML integration (headroom/transforms/kompress_compressor.py)
